'''Cloak Group''' was a group of four [[Gamma-class ATR-6 assault transport|''Gamma''-class ATR-6 assault transports]] in the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]]. These ships were part of the [[Battle of the Anoat Main Sensor Array|attack]] on Sensor Relay Station [[IOS 24]]. Their role was to jam the communications to prevent the station from calling in reinforcements. Whatever became of them afterwards is unknown.

